aat-vimrc (2026.06.18-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Updated README to reflect personal fork of amix/vimrc.
  * Removed amix branding from vimrc source file headers.
  * Added C/C++ plugins: vim-cpp-enhanced-highlight, vim-clang-format.
  * Added Zig language support via zig.vim.
  * Added GDB integration via built-in termdebug.
  * Added vim-dispatch for async make and quickfix navigation.
  * Configured ALE linters for C and C++ (gcc/clang, clangtidy).
  * Added vim-go for full Go language support (goimports, go-to-definition, docs, run/build/test).
  * Added LSP stack: vim-lsp, asyncomplete.vim, asyncomplete-lsp.vim, vim-lsp-settings.

